end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

	nPillars = nPillars + 1
	
	if nPillars == 1 then
		Hydra.ActorEnable(tTrickleSpawner[1])
	end
	
	if nPillars == 3 then
		Hydra.ActorDisable(tTrickleSpawner[1])
	end
end

function Start()

-- Enable pillars
	for i, idPillars in ipairs( Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hell_Lair_Pillars")) do 
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idPillars, true)
		Hydra.ActorSetTeam(idPillars, Hydra.TEAM_MONSTER_DEFAULT)
	end

	tTrickleSpawner = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hell_Lair_PillarsTrickleSpawner")

end
